"How Much Is My Carbon Footprint?"

a web app that allows users to see their greenhouse gas or C0â‚‚ contribution and suggest users informations based on their inputs.

OBJECTIVE
    
    - Empower individuals and businesses to monitor, reduce, and offset their carbon footprint.
    - Provides tracking of carbon emissions based on user activities.
    - Offer actionable recommendations to encourage sustainable lifestyle choices.
    - Support global climate action (SDG 13) by reducing greenhouse gas emissions.
    - Promote responsible consumption (SDG 12) through eco-conscious decision-making.


